MAIN-PARA  (25 statements, depth=4)
PARAGRAPH
├── PERFORM_THRU: PERFORM 1000-INITIALIZE THRU 1000-EXIT
├── PERFORM_THRU: PERFORM 2000-FIND-NEXT-AUTH-SUMMARY THRU 2000-EXIT
