│   │   └── MOVE: MOVE 0 TO WS-AUTH-SMRY-PROC-CNT
│   └── PERFORM_THRU: PERFORM 2000-FIND-NEXT-AUTH-SUMMARY THRU 2000-EXIT
├── PERFORM_THRU: PERFORM 9000-TAKE-CHECKPOINT THRU 9000-EXIT
